<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Defect" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Defect,</orth> 1) fault, imperfection: <cit><quote>having no --s, why dost abhor me?</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 138" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 138</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. son 49.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 49, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 5.70.1" default="NO" valid="yes">70, 1</bibl>. Tp. III, <bibl n="shak. err 1.44.1" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 44</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.124" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 2, 124</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.7.160" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 7, 160</bibl>. Troil. I. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.3.172" default="NO" valid="yes">3, 172</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.4.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 4, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.102" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 102</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.1.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 1, 22</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 2.2.55" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 2, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 2.2.55" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 2, 55</bibl> <emph>d. of sth.</emph> == want of sth.: <cit><quote>d. of that we have,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 151" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 151</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>d. of spirit,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 151" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 151</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>of manners,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.1.184" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 1, 184</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>of judgment,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 4.7.39" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. IV, 7, 39</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.111" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 2, 111</bibl>.<lb />2) deficiency: <cit><quote>all my best doth worship thy d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 149.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 149, 11</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>our will became the servant to d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 2.1.18" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 1, 18</bibl></cit>.
<lb />Misapplied: <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.40" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 1, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.2.152" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 2, 152</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>